msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/date"
msgid "June 26th, 1941 - Grodno, Belorussian SSR."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/failmedic"
msgid "Your medic was not fast enough and the soldier bled to death."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/lose"
msgid "You lost all your men!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/minedetect1"
msgid "There you go! The first mine popped up. I'm sure there's more!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/minedetect2"
msgid "Alright, I think that's all of them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/name"
msgid "Tutorial 5: Trial by Fire"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/name_big"
msgid "Trial by Fire"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/hints/foxhole"
msgid "When the terrain will not give you cover, you should dig your own entrenchments. Soldiers require a foxhole shovel to dig. There is a \"fortifications\" submenu on the bottom right where you can choose what to build. Engineers can erect a wider range of items."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/hints/medic"
msgid "Medics are one of the most valuable assets on the battlefield. They are the only ones who can treat bleeding soldiers. While having a medic selected, hover over an injured soldier and you will be prompted to treat him. Bear in mind, bleeding soldiers will die if left unattended for too long..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/hints/minedetector"
msgid "You must use a mine detector to locate mines. To do so, grab it from the truck's inventory. Once in your soldiers' inventory, you will be able to sweep a specific location using the 'mine detection' button inside the 'item options' submenu on the bottom right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/hints/repair"
msgid "Repair kits are inside each vehicle. If you run out of repair kits, you will have to scavenge for them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/hints/repair2"
msgid "There is ammunition dispersed among crates. To refuel, you need to bring in a fuel truck close to the vehicle or alternatively scavenge for fuel using a jerrycan which can be found inside the vehicle."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/hints/plantmines"
msgid "To mine an area, click the \"AT Mine\" or \"AP Mine\" icons in the \"Items\" menu. Point to the area by left-clicking anywhere on the map. Holding shift and point will queue planting mines in various locations. Holding the left-click and dragging the cursor allows placing a number of mines in a line. Your soldier will start mining from his location in the direction of the click. It takes a soldier a few moments to plant each mine, AT-mines take longer to plant for example."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/officer/defend"
msgid "Here they come! Hold your ground!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/officer/defend2"
msgid "Excellent work, Soldiers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/officer/die1"
msgid "We're engaged! Get down, everybody! Some Soviet border patrol must have heard us!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/officer/die2"
msgid "We will provide suppressive fire! MEDIC! Take care of that man!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/officer/dig"
msgid "They know we're here, and more patrols must be on their way. We will fend off any counter-attack! Dig foxholes, move it! If you need more shovels, there's more in the truck."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/officer/end"
msgid "Area cleared! Excellent job. You are making the fatherland proud!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/officer/repairtank1"
msgid "It wasn't hard to make them talk. Apparently, Ivan has yet another platoon in the northern part of the village. Our orders are to take them out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/officer/repairtank2"
msgid "Wait a moment... That tank looks operational. We should attempt to repair and service it. It will make our job much easier!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/officer/repairtank3"
msgid ""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/officer/start1"
msgid "Damn! Mines! Get out! "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/officer/start1_2"
msgid "The truck is done. We will continue on foot and start by demining this road."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/officer/start2"
msgid "You! Grab a mine detector from the truck and sweep the road ahead!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/officer/tank"
msgid "This thing has no ammo, no fuel! What a bloody disaster. You'll need to stock her up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/officer/village"
msgid "I need you to take your half of the squad and flank the village from the north. Get those bastards from the side and grenade them out of their festering stinkholes. We will keep them spotted and have their guns pointed this way!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/officer/village1"
msgid "Get to cover! We're being fired upon from the village!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/officer/village2"
msgid "Damn it! We were supposed to secure this area without much opposition! The invasion has not taken these communists by surprise! They seem to have a whole detachment in that village. They've fortified their position with MGs."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/place"
msgid "7th Infantry Division."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/story"
msgid "Try your hand at commanding troops and vehicles in your baptism of fire."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/task1"
msgid "Clear out the mines."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/task1_2"
msgid "Treat the bleeding soldier!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/task2"
msgid "Hold your position against the counterattack."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/task3"
msgid "Dig at least 2 foxholes and prepare to repel any counterattacks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/task4"
msgid "Flank the village, take out all the MGs and neutralize the perimeter."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/task5"
msgid "Service the abandoned armored vehicle"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/task6"
msgid "Drive the enemy out of the entire settlement."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/task7"
msgid "Mine the road in preparation for the enemy convoy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/task8"
msgid "Eliminate the enemy convoy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/task_ap"
msgid "Plant at least 10 AP mines in this area!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/task_at"
msgid "Plant at least 10 AT mines in this area!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/officer/convoy"
msgid "A Russian convoy will soon be traveling along the eastern road from the north. Mine the road across the bridge!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/officer/plantmines"
msgid "Soldiers, grab both antipersonnel and anti-tank mines from the truck. Plant each at the marked locations!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/timerconvoy"
msgid "<c(ffff00)>The Russian convoy arrives in:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/timerconvoywarn"
msgid "<c(ff4200)>The Russian convoy arrives in:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/status_ap_mines"
msgid "You planted %1%/10 AP mines in the ordered area."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/status_at_mines"
msgid "You planted %1%/10 AT mines in the ordered area."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/officer/reinforcements"
msgid "Here are your reinforcements. Better late than never..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/narrator/officer/attackconvoy"
msgid "A convoy is approaching! Stay down and hide, allow them to drive into the minefield before attacking!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/outro_completed"
msgid "Well done soldier. You survived your first battle. Looks like we will be able to count on you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/2-combat/outro_failed"
msgid "Make sure you follow orders and make sure you do it quickly. You don't want to end up in a Strafbatalion!"
msgstr ""
